text: is a Japanese football player. She played for the Japan national team. ==Biography== Nakamura was born in Iwate Prefecture on August 3, 1991. After graduating from Tokiwagi Gakuen High School, she joined Albirex Niigata in 2010. She played 118 matches in 11 seasons. In 2021, she moved to new club Sanfrecce Hiroshima Regina.Sanfrecce Hiroshima In 2017, Nakamura was selected the Japan national team for 2017 Algarve Cup. At this competition, on March 3, she debuted against Iceland.
